OL,3,CChancellor faces calls for wealth tax
OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has been urged to tax
OL,7,Fthe rich as she prepares to deliver
OL,8,Fher second Budget.
OL,10,FThe Chancellor is widely expected to
OL,11,Fraise taxes on November 26 in order to
OL,12,Ffill a multibillion-pound gap in her
OL,13,Fspending plans, but is reported to
OL,14,Fhave ruled out a manifesto-busting
OL,15,Fincome tax hike.
