OL,3,CChancellor faces calls for wealth tax
OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FA week before the Budget, opposition
OL,7,Fpoliticians, think tanks and campaign
OL,8,Fgroups have called on the Chancellor
OL,9,Fto focus her plans on the wealthiest
OL,10,Finstead of pursuing broad-based tax
OL,11,Frises.
OL,13,FThey include new Green Party leader
OL,14,FZack Polanski, who said Ms Reeves'
OL,15,Fstatement "must be a cost-of-living
OL,16,FBudget to slash people's bills and
OL,17,Fmake our country affordable again".
