OL,3,CChancellor faces calls for wealth tax
OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Chancellor, Mr
OL,7,FPolanski and other leading Greens
OL,8,Fcalled for a wealth tax along with
OL,9,Fchanges to capital gains tax to bring
OL,10,Fit in line with income tax.
OL,12,FThey also called for wide-ranging
OL,13,Fmeasures to cut energy bills, control
OL,14,Frents and abolish the two-child
OL,15,Fbenefit cap.
OL,17,FMr Polanski said: "Our message to
OL,18,FRachel Reeves is simple: cut bills,
OL,19,Ftax billionaires."
