OL,3,CChancellor faces calls for wealth tax
OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FThe Greens have proposed a 1% tax on
OL,7,Fwealth above #10 million, rising to 2%
OL,8,Fon wealth of more than #1 billion,
OL,9,Fclaiming this will raise #14.8 billion
OL,10,Fa year.
OL,12,FBut experts at Tax Policy Associates
OL,13,Fhave argued such a tax would be "high-
OL,14,Frisk" and could raise much less while
OL,15,Fcausing significant damage to growth.
