OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FCalls for a wealth tax have also been
OL,7,Fbacked by campaign groups including
OL,8,FGreenpeace, Oxfam and Tax Justice UK,
OL,9,Fwho will present the Chancellor with a
OL,10,Fpetition backing the levy signed by
OL,11,F575,000 people on Wednesday.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, think tank IPPR said the
OL,14,FChancellor needed to "pick the right
OL,15,Ffights" at the Budget by taxing people
OL,16,Fwith "unfair advantages and profits"
OL,17,Fbefore raising money from "working
OL,18,Fhouseholds".
