OL,3,CChancellor faces calls for wealth tax
OL,4,Ca week before second Budget
OL,6,FThe think tank, which has been
OL,7,Finfluential in Labour policy-making,
OL,8,Fsaid the Chancellor should reform
OL,9,Fproperty taxes, raising council tax on
OL,10,Fthe most valuable homes, and close
OL,11,F"loopholes" in capital gains tax that
OL,12,F"allow income from wealth to be taxed
OL,13,Fmore lightly than earnings from work".
OL,15,FMs Reeves is reported to have told a
OL,16,Fgroup of loyalist MPs that she plans
OL,17,Fto raise taxes on the wealthiest,
OL,18,Fincluding through changes to property
OL,19,Flevies.
