OL,6,FThe Chancellor suggested to MPs during
OL,7,Fa reception in Number 11 on Monday
OL,8,Fthat she could increase taxes on the
OL,9,Fmost valuable properties in the
OL,10,Fcountry, according to the i Paper.
OL,12,FIPPR also called for national
OL,13,Finsurance to be levied on landlords
OL,14,Fand a reform of gambling taxes, before
OL,15,Feven considering broader measures such
OL,16,Fas extending the freeze on income tax
OL,17,Fthresholds.
