OL,6,FCarsten Jung, executive director at
OL,7,FIPPR, said the Chancellor should
OL,8,F"launch 'a war on bills' ` a
OL,9,Frelentless campaign to lower the cost
OL,10,Fof living, picking fights on behalf of
OL,11,Fworking people".
OL,13,FHe said: "This should start with
OL,14,Fenergy, food and council tax. Together
OL,15,Fwith repairing public services, this
OL,16,FBudget can be living proof that the
OL,17,FGovernment is on people's side."
